launch a web browser
    -conf-browser       whether to use firefox or chromium
        conf_web_browser_browser

    -remote-log_debug       enable remote control through chromedp protocol
        web_browser_remote_debug

    -new-private-window create private window
        _WEB_BROWSER_NEW_PRIVATE_WINDOW

    -http-proxy         address of http proxy server to use
        web_browser_http_proxy

    -socks-proxy        address of socks proxy server to use
        _WEB_BROWSER_SOCKS_PROXY
